<h2><a id="cf" name="cf"></a>Section II: Current Faculty –  Adding or Dropping an Administrative Role</h2>
<table class="featuretable" style="height: 334px" border="0" width="956" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: center" valign="top" width="336"><strong>Campus Policy &amp; Procedure/</strong><strong>University Statute</strong></td>
<td style="text-align: center" valign="top" width="107"><strong>Process Flow</strong></td>
<td style="text-align: center" valign="top" width="175"><strong>Requir</strong><strong>e</strong><strong>d</strong><br />
<strong>Forms &amp; Letters</strong></td>
<td style="text-align: center" valign="top" width="200"><strong>Deadlines &amp; </strong><strong>Due Dates</strong></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: left" valign="top" width="336"><a href="https://faculty.uic.edu/files/2014/07/114-Administrative-Faculty-JD_UIC_FINAL.pdf" target="_blank">Administrative Appointment</a></td>
